WEBVTT

01:39.550 --> 01:43.610
[Road to Success]

01:44.740 --> 01:47.880
[Episode 6]

01:48.280 --> 01:48.870
Blazed over the bar.

01:48.870 --> 01:50.350
Excuse me. Thank you.

01:51.400 --> 01:52.660
Straight into the net.

01:53.000 --> 01:53.759
Boss,

01:53.759 --> 01:54.759
I want some boiled fist-shaped meatballs

01:54.759 --> 01:55.840
with popsicles later.

01:55.840 --> 01:57.509
-Weren't we going anyway?
-Let's go get popsicles.

01:57.509 --> 01:59.110
Let's go buy some popsicles.

01:59.150 --> 01:59.710
Hurry up.

02:00.760 --> 02:02.000
I'm going first. I'll order for us.

02:02.000 --> 02:02.950
I'm coming with you.

02:02.950 --> 02:03.850
Let's go.

02:04.590 --> 02:05.640
-You don't say...
-Ma'am!

02:05.640 --> 02:08.240
-Five orders of fist-shaped meatballs!
-I want a popsicle.

02:08.240 --> 02:09.680
-And a few popsicles.
-Get me a mung bean one.

02:09.680 --> 02:10.800
Boss, what flavor do you want?

02:10.800 --> 02:12.520
-Mung bean.
-Mung bean.

02:12.520 --> 02:14.360
-Two mung bean ones.
-Mung bean flavor again?

02:14.360 --> 02:15.840
I just love this.

02:15.840 --> 02:17.440
Thank you. Thank you, ma'am.

02:18.960 --> 02:19.800
Here it comes.

02:19.800 --> 02:20.710
Fresh out of the pot.

02:20.710 --> 02:21.560
Still piping hot.

02:21.560 --> 02:22.400
Come on.

02:23.150 --> 02:24.870
Did you guys see the message
in the group chat?

02:24.870 --> 02:27.400
Our next opponent is
Lyujing International.

02:27.870 --> 02:28.750
Let me say this in advance:

02:28.750 --> 02:30.210
I'm not playing that game.

02:30.520 --> 02:32.579
Well, since it's Lyujing International,

02:32.579 --> 02:35.040
does that mean
Jiang Tianyu will be playing?

02:35.190 --> 02:35.910
Yes.

02:37.710 --> 02:38.560
Don't let me run into that brat.

02:38.560 --> 02:40.079
If I do, I'll definitely beat him up.

02:40.079 --> 02:41.520
Fu treated him so well,

02:41.520 --> 02:42.980
and he just left like that.

02:44.980 --> 02:47.240
It's fine. He's just an ungrateful jerk.

02:53.050 --> 02:54.890
[One and a half years earlier—
second semester of 10th grade]

02:55.870 --> 02:57.700
Hurry up. Stop dawdling.

02:58.280 --> 02:59.640
Where are you going, Fu?

03:01.970 --> 03:03.280
-You two, get over here. Quick!
-Jiang Tianyu.

03:03.280 --> 03:04.190
Come back.

03:04.520 --> 03:06.530
I'm busy handling my transfer procedures.

03:06.530 --> 03:08.430
I don't have time to argue with you.

03:08.430 --> 03:09.960
Do you really have to leave?

03:10.030 --> 03:10.960
Coach Jiang isn't

03:10.960 --> 03:12.150
coaching us anymore,

03:12.150 --> 03:13.560
but we still have Mr. Li.

03:13.910 --> 03:15.080
The school hasn't given up on us,

03:15.080 --> 03:17.010
which means we still have a chance.

03:17.079 --> 03:17.840
Mr. Li?

03:18.910 --> 03:20.240
He's a track and field teacher.

03:20.240 --> 03:22.240
He doesn't even have
a soccer coaching license.

03:22.240 --> 03:24.000
You seriously plan to keep
kicking a ball around with him forever?

03:24.000 --> 03:25.730
I want professional training,

03:25.750 --> 03:27.150
not to waste my time here.

03:27.360 --> 03:28.450
If we don't have
a professional football coach,

03:28.450 --> 03:29.780
we can find another one.

03:29.800 --> 03:30.560
But if you leave,

03:30.560 --> 03:32.430
this team will really fall apart.

03:32.430 --> 03:33.590
So be it.

03:33.590 --> 03:34.840
That's none of my business.

03:34.840 --> 03:36.900
I'm transferring, and that's final.

03:37.430 --> 03:40.120
We've played football together
for over three years.

03:40.120 --> 03:41.280
Does this team really mean

03:41.280 --> 03:42.940
nothing to you at all?

03:42.960 --> 03:43.940
To me,

03:44.520 --> 03:46.520
getting into high school
as a soccer recruit

03:46.520 --> 03:48.960
and being scouted
by Lyujing International—

03:48.960 --> 03:50.160
that's what matters.

03:51.710 --> 03:52.520
Fu,

03:53.000 --> 03:53.910
don't try

03:53.910 --> 03:56.310
pulling some team-spirit guilt trip on me.

03:56.800 --> 03:58.200
That means nothing to me.

04:14.600 --> 04:15.650
♪ As time goes by ♪

04:16.529 --> 04:18.160
♪ Nothing remains ♪

04:18.160 --> 04:19.480
I'll get you a new one, Boss.

04:19.200 --> 04:21.779
♪ Those in the dream
refuse to wake alone ♪

04:22.780 --> 04:24.160
♪ The shadow is above ♪

04:25.270 --> 04:26.930
♪ Rain falls all around ♪

04:27.560 --> 04:28.260
♪ In your arms ♪

04:28.310 --> 04:29.630
Do you know how fast he was?

04:29.170 --> 04:30.540
♪ We become one ♪

04:31.110 --> 04:32.650
♪ Day and night ♪

04:32.040 --> 04:34.070
And this guy Chen Chongzhi is so cool—

04:33.370 --> 04:35.740
♪ I can see you ♪

04:34.070 --> 04:35.950
he just did a backhand slash,

04:35.950 --> 04:37.360
whoosh,

04:36.710 --> 04:38.950
♪ With my eyes ♪

04:37.360 --> 04:39.750
and sliced right through his shoe sole.

04:39.670 --> 04:41.300
♪ Just hold me tight ♪

04:39.750 --> 04:40.950
Sliced the shoe sole?

04:40.950 --> 04:43.159
Really, it was just an inch away.

04:41.960 --> 04:47.300
♪ Looking into my soul ♪

04:43.159 --> 04:43.950
An inch?

04:43.950 --> 04:44.750
How long is an inch?

04:44.750 --> 04:46.270
An inch... An inch...

04:46.270 --> 04:47.120
We're here to return the balls.

04:47.120 --> 04:48.870
Just about this long.

04:48.530 --> 04:49.930
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

04:48.870 --> 04:50.920
Then all of a sudden,

04:50.670 --> 04:51.810
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

04:50.920 --> 04:52.480
everyone in the hall...

04:52.870 --> 04:54.310
Coach is actually still here.

04:52.990 --> 04:53.760
♪ Wonderful dreams ♪

04:54.740 --> 04:56.090
♪ Are so close to me ♪

04:56.480 --> 04:57.920
I think
there's something wrong with his brain.

04:57.440 --> 04:58.330
♪ Memories fly ♪

04:57.920 --> 04:59.120
Why do you care?

04:59.190 --> 05:00.440
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

04:59.920 --> 05:01.870
I'm definitely not going over there
and getting embarrassed.

05:01.450 --> 05:07.050
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

05:01.870 --> 05:03.070
On a day this hot,

05:03.070 --> 05:05.870
I'd rather go back to the classroom
and enjoy the air conditioning.

05:05.870 --> 05:07.510
-True. Let's go
-Come on!

05:09.630 --> 05:10.240
Keep reading, Boss.

05:10.240 --> 05:11.190
I'll keep going then.

05:11.190 --> 05:13.190
Chen Chongzhi pushed the door open
and went in,

05:13.190 --> 05:16.120
and dozens of people inside
immediately stood up...

05:39.630 --> 05:42.240
Looks like
your coaching isn't going so well.

05:44.190 --> 05:45.320
It's going alright.

05:45.510 --> 05:48.040
You're really just going to
sit here and wait?

05:50.830 --> 05:53.000
I'm showing my sincerity.

05:54.680 --> 05:57.190
Don't you want to know them inside out

05:57.190 --> 05:58.510
and win them over?

06:01.680 --> 06:03.430
I heard they were really strong

06:03.430 --> 06:04.310
back in middle school

06:04.310 --> 06:06.110
and even finished as runner-up.

06:08.310 --> 06:10.240
Only champions deserve to be remembered,

06:10.240 --> 06:11.190
Ms. Lin.

06:11.630 --> 06:14.560
Is winning the championship
really that important?

06:16.360 --> 06:18.420
I've asked myself that question too.

06:20.480 --> 06:22.430
But you're calmer than I expected.

06:23.240 --> 06:24.240
Aren't you worried

06:24.240 --> 06:26.040
I'll ruin your team and leave you

06:26.070 --> 06:28.400
unable to explain yourself to the school?

06:30.360 --> 06:31.870
Trust the people you employ;

06:31.870 --> 06:33.159
don't employ those you distrust.

06:33.159 --> 06:34.960
I believe you have your reasons.

06:39.040 --> 06:39.720
Okay.

06:46.120 --> 06:47.870
Their next opponent has been announced.

06:47.870 --> 06:49.530
It's Lyujing International.

07:03.310 --> 07:04.910
Keep your posture straight.

07:05.000 --> 07:05.750
That's right.

07:05.750 --> 07:06.680
Go.

07:08.080 --> 07:09.560
His records are
all at the Academic Affairs Office.

07:09.560 --> 07:10.430
-Everything's been prepared.
-All prepared?

07:10.430 --> 07:11.240
Yes, that's right.

07:11.240 --> 07:12.390
Thanks for your trouble.

07:12.390 --> 07:12.750
Not at all.

07:12.750 --> 07:13.630
It's nothing.

07:13.950 --> 07:15.680
-Nice campus.
-Coach.

07:16.190 --> 07:17.750
I'll go say hi to some old friends first.

07:17.750 --> 07:18.870
Okay, go ahead.

07:20.120 --> 07:20.920
Let's go.

07:20.920 --> 07:21.600
Okay.

07:21.600 --> 07:23.600
-You guys go first.
-That's enough.

07:27.680 --> 07:28.630
Long time no see.

07:30.680 --> 07:31.680
Long time no see.

07:33.750 --> 07:35.210
Captain Jiang of Lyujing,

07:36.070 --> 07:37.750
what brings you to our school?

07:38.950 --> 07:40.159
I came with my coach today

07:40.159 --> 07:41.800
to pick up my freshman-year records.

07:41.800 --> 07:42.800
Figured I'd check out

07:42.800 --> 07:44.600
my next opponent while I'm at it.

07:45.870 --> 07:46.870
Our Coach Ma

07:47.750 --> 07:50.409
won the city's
Best Youth Football Coach award.

07:50.800 --> 07:52.200
Pretty impressive, huh?

07:55.800 --> 07:57.270
So who's your coach now?

07:58.000 --> 07:59.000
We...

08:04.160 --> 08:05.120
Don't tell me you don't even

08:05.120 --> 08:06.480
have a coach now.

08:09.780 --> 08:10.930
So pitiful.

08:11.560 --> 08:13.190
Good thing I transferred early.

08:13.190 --> 08:14.560
Otherwise, I'd be stuck like you guys—

08:14.560 --> 08:15.950
going nowhere in football

08:15.950 --> 08:17.120
and just being losers.

08:17.120 --> 08:18.510
-You...
-Who are you calling losers?

08:18.510 --> 08:19.630
Watch your mouth.

08:19.630 --> 08:21.750
Whoever doesn't have a coach is a loser.

08:21.750 --> 08:22.880
Wouldn't you agree,

08:23.000 --> 08:24.460
Team Hongjing's Captain?

08:27.560 --> 08:28.400
Who hit me?

08:33.679 --> 08:35.130
You dare call him a loser?

08:42.730 --> 08:43.730
Am I wrong?

08:44.090 --> 08:45.750
You're just a bunch of losers.

08:48.910 --> 08:49.870
Jiang Tianyu,

08:49.870 --> 08:51.240
don't go too far.

08:52.270 --> 08:54.000
Trash talk doesn't prove anything.

08:54.000 --> 08:55.600
Let's settle it on the field.

09:00.960 --> 09:01.550
Alright.

09:02.240 --> 09:03.000
You two,

09:03.000 --> 09:04.000
mark me together.

09:07.120 --> 09:07.720
I'll do it.

10:33.840 --> 10:34.570
Pass it here!

10:41.320 --> 10:42.390
Nice shot!

10:48.720 --> 10:49.720
Keep it up!

10:50.510 --> 10:51.270
That was so cool!

10:51.270 --> 10:52.200
One more!

10:52.200 --> 10:53.270
Amazing!

10:53.270 --> 10:54.320
One more!

10:54.790 --> 10:55.670
One more!

10:59.550 --> 11:00.440
Thank you.

11:05.240 --> 11:07.000
-Well done, Fu!
-Fu!

11:07.000 --> 11:08.000
That was so cool!

11:08.000 --> 11:09.510
-How was I?
-Nice pass.

11:09.720 --> 11:11.240
From Lyujing, right?

11:12.150 --> 11:14.150
I'm Wang Fa, football coach

11:15.120 --> 11:16.780
of Hongjing No. 8 High School.

11:17.790 --> 11:18.450
I'm Coach Ma

11:18.600 --> 11:19.270
of Lyujing.

11:53.320 --> 11:54.720
So patient.

12:09.750 --> 12:11.270
Sitting there again, as expected.

12:11.270 --> 12:13.270
At this exact time, as always.

12:17.750 --> 12:19.030
Yesterday, you told me

12:19.030 --> 12:20.120
he looked very sincere

12:20.120 --> 12:21.360
when he said he was our coach.

12:21.360 --> 12:22.120
Really?

12:22.120 --> 12:24.000
Really, I saw it with my own eyes.

12:24.000 --> 12:25.030
They were both there.

12:25.030 --> 12:26.960
Wen Chengye was pretty
impressive yesterday, stepping up.

12:26.960 --> 12:29.000
All of them are acting so mysterious.

12:29.000 --> 12:30.330
I can't figure them out.

12:31.870 --> 12:33.400
Why don't we just go ask him?

12:42.210 --> 12:44.150
Yesterday, he admitted
that he's our coach.

12:44.150 --> 12:45.200
That at least proves

12:45.200 --> 12:46.660
he never looked down on us.

12:46.840 --> 12:47.480
Right?

12:49.510 --> 12:51.150
Actually, I just don't get it.

12:51.150 --> 12:52.870
He sits here every day.

12:52.890 --> 12:54.870
He can't possibly be
just sitting here watching.

12:54.870 --> 12:55.630
Right?

13:00.320 --> 13:00.790
Go.

13:01.600 --> 13:02.080
Wait...

13:02.360 --> 13:03.000
Chen.

13:03.480 --> 13:05.940
-Are we really doing this?
-Let's go. Hurry.

13:11.420 --> 13:12.140
Ms. Lin...

13:27.600 --> 13:28.480
Um...

13:30.120 --> 13:32.120
Let's have Fu Xinshu say a few words.

13:37.270 --> 13:39.320
These kids are so cute.

13:41.600 --> 13:42.270
Coach,

13:42.720 --> 13:43.600
no matter what,

13:44.030 --> 13:46.740
we shouldn't have missed
the last three days of training.

13:46.740 --> 13:47.510
We're sorry.

13:59.550 --> 14:00.440
The main thing is, we don't understand

14:00.440 --> 14:01.530
the training you assigned,

14:01.530 --> 14:02.480
and you didn't seem to

14:02.480 --> 14:03.750
want to explain it at all.

14:03.750 --> 14:05.510
Yeah, we were all exhausted,

14:05.510 --> 14:06.720
while you and Ms. Lin

14:06.720 --> 14:08.520
were eating chips so leisurely.

14:09.150 --> 14:11.010
Anyone would've snapped, right?

14:20.000 --> 14:20.750
Hey,

14:21.270 --> 14:22.330
why did you do that?

14:22.600 --> 14:23.910
Were you like everyone else,

14:23.910 --> 14:25.000
looking down on us,

14:25.000 --> 14:27.270
so you just brushed us off
with random drills?

14:27.270 --> 14:28.270
What do you think?

14:30.030 --> 14:31.700
Why would I ask if I knew?

14:31.730 --> 14:32.480
Coach,

14:33.000 --> 14:35.060
were you deliberately torturing us?

14:36.790 --> 14:37.920
Deliberately? Yes.

14:38.360 --> 14:40.960
But whether that was torture
is open to debate.

14:44.750 --> 14:45.320
Coach,

14:45.320 --> 14:46.870
can you tell us why?

14:46.870 --> 14:49.330
Just why did you arrange
that jogging drill?

14:55.150 --> 14:57.480
I've been waiting for you to ask me that.

14:57.480 --> 14:59.360
Why didn't any of you ask me
before training started?

14:59.360 --> 15:00.200
Well,

15:00.440 --> 15:02.000
wasn't that your order?

15:02.000 --> 15:02.630
What,

15:02.630 --> 15:04.150
you expected us to go against you?

15:04.150 --> 15:05.750
Yeah, you're the coach.

15:05.750 --> 15:08.350
It's impolite for us
to ask too many questions.

15:08.360 --> 15:09.840
We figured
we should just do what you told us.

15:09.840 --> 15:11.390
Can being polite win games?

15:18.950 --> 15:20.580
You didn't agree with my instructions,

15:20.580 --> 15:21.440
yet you followed them anyway.

15:21.440 --> 15:22.840
What's the point of that?

15:24.150 --> 15:25.720
Coach, you mean

15:25.720 --> 15:27.960
y-you want us to assess your instructions?

15:27.960 --> 15:28.720
Yes.

15:29.840 --> 15:31.840
Blind obedience makes people numb.

15:32.470 --> 15:33.440
On the field,

15:33.870 --> 15:35.360
if players only follow orders

15:35.360 --> 15:36.550
without thinking for themselves,

15:36.550 --> 15:37.840
that's a crime.

15:49.640 --> 15:51.370
Bring your brains to training.

15:51.870 --> 15:53.940
Don't blindly submit to
your coach's authority.

15:53.940 --> 15:55.680
Understand the purpose behind every drill.

15:55.680 --> 15:56.920
Most importantly,

15:56.960 --> 16:00.020
learn to ask questions
and challenge what you're told.

16:06.870 --> 16:08.670
That's all for the first lesson.

16:08.930 --> 16:11.500
If anyone still thinks
I'm looking down on you

16:11.610 --> 16:12.910
or torturing you,

16:13.750 --> 16:15.810
you don't need to come back tomorrow.

16:24.120 --> 16:24.960
Ms. Lin,

16:25.860 --> 16:27.390
what are you smiling about?

16:30.550 --> 16:31.410
I'm not.

16:31.510 --> 16:32.240
You are.

16:32.240 --> 16:32.960
Definitely.

16:32.960 --> 16:34.030
Right, Chen?

16:34.840 --> 16:35.600
You smiled,

16:35.620 --> 16:37.350
though it wasn't very obvious.

16:37.600 --> 16:38.510
I just think

16:38.510 --> 16:41.600
Coach Wang's first lesson
is right up my alley.

17:28.000 --> 17:29.130
What a coincidence.

17:34.750 --> 17:36.010
Actually,

17:36.350 --> 17:37.810
I want to apologize to you.

17:39.160 --> 17:40.310
I said,

17:40.310 --> 17:42.000
I want to apologize to you!

17:42.590 --> 17:43.480
For what?

17:44.960 --> 17:46.310
Before yesterday,

17:46.310 --> 17:47.550
I thought

17:47.640 --> 17:49.640
you didn't really want to coach them.

17:49.640 --> 17:50.720
You were just

17:50.720 --> 17:52.450
fooling around to brush me off.

17:53.790 --> 17:55.720
First, I never go back on my word.

17:56.750 --> 17:58.810
And I don't like brushing people off.

17:59.790 --> 18:00.820
A promise to you

18:00.960 --> 18:02.640
is a promise to myself.

18:05.990 --> 18:07.230
But you, Ms. Lin,

18:07.790 --> 18:09.720
don't forget what you promised me.

18:11.480 --> 18:12.640
Don't worry.

18:12.640 --> 18:14.410
I've got that firmly in mind.

18:14.480 --> 18:15.590
I'll settle everything

18:15.590 --> 18:17.050
with you before the match.

18:18.880 --> 18:20.510
Good night, Coach.

18:23.310 --> 18:25.070
What's with that cool-guy act?

18:42.550 --> 18:43.920
They're still not here.

18:46.960 --> 18:48.510
You're the team supervisor.

18:48.510 --> 18:50.170
What do you think we should do?

19:07.270 --> 19:10.070
Well, rain's gonna fall,
and people gotta eat.

19:11.030 --> 19:13.510
It's still two hours until dinner.

19:14.960 --> 19:16.960
Afternoon tea is an indispensable meal

19:16.960 --> 19:19.090
in the history of human civilization.

19:20.550 --> 19:21.440
Gently, gently.

19:21.440 --> 19:22.270
Give me another one.

19:22.270 --> 19:23.440
-Don't rush him.
-Get another one.

19:23.440 --> 19:24.590
Don't rush me.

19:24.830 --> 19:26.070
-Will this work?
-Keep your hands steady!

19:26.070 --> 19:27.030
Try a thinner one.

19:27.030 --> 19:28.920
There's a mosquito. Help me swat it.

19:28.920 --> 19:30.050
There's a mosquito.

19:30.480 --> 19:31.070
Just ignore it.

19:31.070 --> 19:31.510
Use that one.

19:31.510 --> 19:33.070
Hurry up, bro.

19:33.070 --> 19:34.960
-Qin Ao, stop nudging me!
-Coach is already there!

19:34.960 --> 19:36.480
-Let's go! Hurry!
-Hurry.

19:36.480 --> 19:37.680
Coach's already there.
Stop fiddling with it.

19:37.680 --> 19:38.240
-Let's go.
-Go, go, go.

19:38.240 --> 19:39.310
-Let's go.
-Hurry.

19:39.330 --> 19:40.350
-Let's go.
-Hurry.

19:40.350 --> 19:41.550
-We're late.
-Hurry.

19:41.550 --> 19:42.830
Your boys are here.

19:42.830 --> 19:43.880
We're a bit short on time.

19:43.880 --> 19:46.750
-Coach.
-Hello, Coach. Hello, Ms. Lin.

19:48.510 --> 19:49.510
Coach,

19:49.510 --> 19:50.200
well...

19:51.750 --> 19:52.720
Sorry.

19:53.000 --> 19:54.030
We were a bit loud yesterday.

19:54.030 --> 19:55.030
We apologize.

20:10.070 --> 20:13.670
Coach, it gets really awkward for us
when you don't say anything.

20:14.720 --> 20:15.640
You're late.

20:22.350 --> 20:23.310
But thank you.

20:25.000 --> 20:27.000
Coach, we have something for you.

20:27.830 --> 20:29.760
This was Coach Jiang's stopwatch.

20:35.920 --> 20:37.310
Ever since we joined the team
in middle school,

20:37.310 --> 20:38.510
he always used it.

20:38.960 --> 20:40.070
After he left,

20:40.070 --> 20:41.400
nobody used it anymore.

20:41.920 --> 20:43.550
It was broken, actually.

20:43.550 --> 20:44.830
We secretly tinkered with it

20:44.830 --> 20:46.480
and managed to fix it.

20:50.270 --> 20:51.790
We even replaced the cord

20:51.790 --> 20:52.550
and cleaned it up really nicely.

20:52.550 --> 20:53.400
Take a look.

20:54.310 --> 20:56.110
You're our new coach from now on.

20:57.000 --> 20:58.510
We hope you'll accept it.

21:17.200 --> 21:18.730
Such an important thing...

21:20.550 --> 21:22.110
I'll keep it safe for you.

21:27.160 --> 21:29.010
Coach, you mean

21:29.040 --> 21:30.270
you won't be staying forever,

21:30.270 --> 21:30.920
right?

21:33.030 --> 21:34.160
I've said it before.

21:34.680 --> 21:36.210
I'm only the interim coach.

21:36.400 --> 21:38.330
I can't promise I'll stay forever.

21:45.550 --> 21:46.550
But

21:47.440 --> 21:48.700
for as long as I'm here,

21:50.310 --> 21:52.040
I'll give it everything I have.

21:55.590 --> 21:56.270
Okay?

21:56.750 --> 21:57.920
-Okay!
-Okay!

21:57.920 --> 21:59.000
We've got a world-class,

21:59.000 --> 21:59.830
-big-shot coach now.
-Great!

21:59.830 --> 22:01.550
And from Nanton!

22:01.550 --> 22:02.510
Then, Coach,

22:02.510 --> 22:03.830
c-can we share

22:03.830 --> 22:04.790
your snacks?

22:04.790 --> 22:06.030
No.

22:06.440 --> 22:07.700
But you can share hers.

22:08.960 --> 22:10.230
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

22:10.250 --> 22:11.240
Ms. Lin.

22:12.440 --> 22:13.770
Ms. Lin.

22:14.270 --> 22:16.230
Then do you have any gifts for me?

22:16.230 --> 22:17.400
Training! Training time!

22:17.400 --> 22:18.460
-Training! Training time!
-Let's go.

22:18.460 --> 22:20.590
Training time! Training time!

22:20.590 --> 22:21.750
Let's go!

22:21.750 --> 22:22.790
Come on.

22:22.790 --> 22:24.050
Let's go. Go get ready.

22:26.110 --> 22:27.160
Let's go. Let's go.

22:27.160 --> 22:28.310
Training time!

22:30.720 --> 22:32.810
Today we're doing 15-meter shuttle runs.

22:32.810 --> 22:33.810
Three sets.

22:33.850 --> 22:35.720
Two minutes' rest between each set.

22:35.720 --> 22:36.960
After that,

22:36.960 --> 22:38.070
30 quick steps in place,

22:38.070 --> 22:40.240
followed by a 20-meter straight sprint.

22:40.240 --> 22:41.640
More running?

22:42.350 --> 22:43.240
Coach,

22:43.510 --> 22:44.750
there's something we forgot to ask.

22:44.750 --> 22:47.010
What's the purpose of today's training?

22:47.310 --> 22:48.070
Fitness.

22:49.030 --> 22:50.880
You guys haven't trained in too long.

22:50.880 --> 22:51.830
Your conditioning is terrible.

22:51.830 --> 22:54.400
Coach, with such high-intensity training,

22:54.400 --> 22:56.440
are you preparing us for the World Cup?

22:56.440 --> 22:57.000
Then let me ask you,

22:57.000 --> 22:58.960
why did you want me to be your coach?

22:58.960 --> 23:01.110
We've got a match in half a month.

23:01.110 --> 23:02.550
Yeah, we figured we'd train hard

23:02.550 --> 23:03.920
and crush our opponents later!

23:03.920 --> 23:05.000
So it's about winning.

23:05.000 --> 23:06.040
-Yeah!
-Winning!

23:06.550 --> 23:08.880
If you want to win, you need to
adapt to match-level intensity.

23:08.880 --> 23:09.310
Take your positions.

23:09.310 --> 23:10.160
-No problem.
-Alright, gather up!

23:10.160 --> 23:10.960
-Okay, let's go.
-Let's go.

23:10.960 --> 23:11.960
-Let's go.
-Gather up.

23:11.960 --> 23:12.590
Training time.

23:12.590 --> 23:13.120
Let's go.

23:13.640 --> 23:14.640
Go, go, go!

23:32.150 --> 23:33.550
Come on, pick up the pace!

23:36.590 --> 23:37.920
Hands touch the ground.

23:40.750 --> 23:41.550
Keep going!

23:41.960 --> 23:43.000
These little brats

23:43.000 --> 23:45.100
sure get fired up during training.

23:45.510 --> 23:46.240
Good thing I

23:46.240 --> 23:47.310
managed to get Wang Fa on board.

23:47.310 --> 23:48.700
Touch the ground!

23:50.200 --> 23:51.270
Last two laps.

23:51.270 --> 23:52.070
Keep going!

23:55.590 --> 23:56.640
Good job, Coach.

23:57.350 --> 23:58.830
Everyone's training so hard.

23:58.830 --> 23:59.680
I suppose

23:59.680 --> 24:01.790
you don't need any help from me, right?

24:01.790 --> 24:03.120
Actually, I do.

24:04.480 --> 24:05.480
What do you mean?

24:07.440 --> 24:08.270
Be my assistant coach.

24:08.270 --> 24:09.480
That's what I mean.

24:09.830 --> 24:12.110
I shouldn't have said anything.

24:12.110 --> 24:14.640
Wang Fa, you're too cruel.

24:21.070 --> 24:22.920
Do you really need me to
wave these little flags to train

24:22.920 --> 24:25.250
their reaction speed and concentration?

24:26.920 --> 24:29.110
Having props makes you feel
more like coaching.

24:29.110 --> 24:30.590
Don't you think, Ms. Lin?

24:54.510 --> 24:58.510
-Thank you, Ms. Lin!
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.

25:00.070 --> 25:01.400
We're heading out, Ms. Lin.

25:01.400 --> 25:03.200
Bye, Ms. Lin. Bye, Coach.

25:03.200 --> 25:03.830
Bye-bye!

25:03.830 --> 25:06.400
-Bye, Coach!
-Bye, Coach.

25:06.400 --> 25:07.440
Treat us to fried skewers!

25:07.440 --> 25:09.240
-Let's go have fried skewers.
-How are they doing?

25:09.240 --> 25:10.270
Then I'm gonna pass.

25:10.270 --> 25:12.240
I have a part-time job tonight.

25:12.240 --> 25:13.500
Their fitness is poor,

25:13.720 --> 25:14.680
but their spirit is commendable.

25:14.680 --> 25:16.200
You're so busy, Fu.

25:16.200 --> 25:18.160
We've still got plenty of time.

25:19.200 --> 25:20.110
Ms. Lin,

25:20.110 --> 25:20.920
Coach.

25:22.240 --> 25:23.510
I've thought about it for a long time—

25:23.510 --> 25:24.750
I probably won't be able to

25:24.750 --> 25:26.550
join future training sessions.

25:26.750 --> 25:27.510
Because

25:27.510 --> 25:30.440
I need to attend
the track and field team's training.

25:32.510 --> 25:33.600
It's easier to get

25:33.620 --> 25:35.480
a high ranking in track and field.

25:35.880 --> 25:37.160
If you're recognized as
a high-level athlete,

25:37.160 --> 25:40.220
you can get extra points
for the college entrance exam.

25:41.340 --> 25:42.420
Actually,

25:42.480 --> 25:44.270
I've had a great time with everyone.

25:44.270 --> 25:44.960
But...

25:44.960 --> 25:45.750
It's okay.

25:46.160 --> 25:47.200
We understand.

25:47.640 --> 25:49.920
A person's time and energy are limited.

25:50.270 --> 25:51.440
Now,

25:51.440 --> 25:53.440
it's time to choose between the two.

25:53.750 --> 25:55.210
We respect your decision.

25:55.510 --> 25:57.590
But before you leave,

25:57.590 --> 25:59.990
shouldn't you say
a proper goodbye to them?

26:00.750 --> 26:01.400
Okay.

26:01.680 --> 26:02.740
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

26:28.920 --> 26:30.250
Something on your mind?

26:33.440 --> 26:35.240
Did I agree too quickly

26:35.520 --> 26:37.610
to let Chen Weidong leave the team?

26:37.640 --> 26:39.970
I should've tried harder to persuade him.

26:41.400 --> 26:43.000
Even if you had,

26:43.210 --> 26:46.140
all that would've done
was make him feel more guilty.

26:46.360 --> 26:48.490
It wouldn't have changed the outcome.

26:49.830 --> 26:50.510
True.

26:51.270 --> 26:52.590
He was only brought in to help

26:52.590 --> 26:54.350
fill out the numbers temporarily anyway.

26:54.350 --> 26:56.030
Lasting this long

26:56.030 --> 26:57.430
was already impressive.

27:04.960 --> 27:06.680
But you're awfully calm about this.

27:06.680 --> 27:08.240
We just lost a player.

27:09.590 --> 27:11.510
I thought you'd already

27:11.830 --> 27:13.350
dumped the team on me.

27:14.440 --> 27:16.770
You still care about such trivial things?

27:17.060 --> 27:19.000
This isn't really a trivial thing, right?

27:19.000 --> 27:21.200
I'm their supervisor after all.

27:21.200 --> 27:23.660
I should at least
pay some attention to them.

27:25.400 --> 27:27.480
But for a team to go far,

27:28.030 --> 27:29.160
relying on substitutes

27:29.160 --> 27:30.960
is never the answer.

27:39.960 --> 27:40.960
Dark chocolate—

27:40.960 --> 27:42.400
zero calories and free.

27:42.400 --> 27:44.000
Please enlighten me, Coach.

27:53.740 --> 27:56.100
How practical of you, Ms. Lin.

27:59.920 --> 28:02.240
Who was the player
Chen Weidong was replacing?

28:02.240 --> 28:03.510
Wen Chengye.

28:03.510 --> 28:05.040
But he probably won't come.

28:05.590 --> 28:07.070
Wen Chengye...

28:12.420 --> 28:14.150
Well, let's see about him then.

28:15.400 --> 28:16.270
Didn't I just say

28:16.270 --> 28:17.510
he probably wouldn't come?

28:17.510 --> 28:18.910
He's a tough nut to crack.

28:19.480 --> 28:21.270
You majored in psychology.

28:21.270 --> 28:22.310
How hard can it be?

28:23.160 --> 28:24.510
You have a point.

28:24.510 --> 28:26.440
Then you'll help me, right, Coach?

28:27.680 --> 28:30.540
That depends on
how much chocolate you've got left.

28:36.830 --> 28:37.440
Lin Lu!

28:37.830 --> 28:38.230
Come on.

28:38.230 --> 28:38.830
Come on!

28:40.400 --> 28:41.640
Come on, come on.

28:43.640 --> 28:44.570
Come on, come on!

28:45.480 --> 28:46.680
It's fine. Again!

28:47.830 --> 28:48.470
How is it?

28:48.480 --> 28:48.850
Next team.

28:48.850 --> 28:51.050
Have they shown any improvement today?

28:51.750 --> 28:52.880
Do you want the truth or a lie?

28:52.880 --> 28:53.720
Take the shot!

28:54.680 --> 28:56.590
It's probably because Chen Weidong
quit the team,

28:56.590 --> 28:58.050
and they're pretty upset.

28:58.270 --> 29:00.550
Anyone easily swayed by outside factors

29:00.550 --> 29:02.010
can't play football well.

29:02.440 --> 29:03.240
Shoot!

29:05.890 --> 29:08.080
They're still kids, after all.

29:06.370 --> 29:07.840
[Zheng Feiyang] [Lin Lu] [Yu Ming]

29:10.550 --> 29:11.740
I think

29:11.920 --> 29:14.920
if the almighty former Nanton coach

29:14.920 --> 29:15.920
could give them

29:15.920 --> 29:17.650
a little bit of encouragement,

29:17.680 --> 29:20.740
-they'd definitely be pumped up.
-You guys are up next.

29:22.830 --> 29:23.640
Quick!

29:26.310 --> 29:28.640
The person we've been waiting for is here.

29:33.310 --> 29:34.110
Qin Ao!

29:40.640 --> 29:42.590
A ragtag bunch like you, and you still

29:42.590 --> 29:44.180
call yourselves a team?

29:44.680 --> 29:45.920
Get out of here.

29:48.350 --> 29:49.160
Don't hold him back.

29:49.160 --> 29:50.160
Am I wrong?

29:50.720 --> 29:51.720
A bunch of losers.

29:54.400 --> 29:55.720
You call us losers?

29:55.740 --> 29:57.540
Like you can play so much better.

30:07.510 --> 30:08.710
-Defense!
-Defense.

30:09.240 --> 30:09.960
Cover him!

30:10.350 --> 30:11.250
Left! Left!

30:17.160 --> 30:19.360
Take it easy! Don't stick your foot out!

30:20.160 --> 30:21.350
-I got it!
-Chase him!

30:21.350 --> 30:22.510
-Double up on him!
-Cut him off!

30:22.510 --> 30:24.440
Cut him off! Don't let him through!

30:24.960 --> 30:26.230
Cut him off! Hurry!

30:26.720 --> 30:27.750
I got him! Let me!

30:28.070 --> 30:28.930
Cut him off!

30:31.550 --> 30:32.110
Cover!

30:33.240 --> 30:34.040
Lin Lu...

30:34.680 --> 30:36.000
-Don't block me!
-Track back!

30:36.000 --> 30:36.790
Watch the ball and track back!

30:36.790 --> 30:37.850
Mark him! Mark him!

30:38.790 --> 30:39.440
I got it!

30:46.030 --> 30:47.160
So what if you have good skills?

30:47.160 --> 30:49.240
If only he could replace Chen Weidong.

30:49.240 --> 30:50.240
We don't need him.

30:56.960 --> 30:57.880
Losers.

30:57.880 --> 30:59.400
Nothing good
ever comes out of your mouth, huh?

30:59.400 --> 31:00.000
Looking to get punched?

31:00.000 --> 31:01.330
-Enough, Qin Ao.
-Boss!

31:01.510 --> 31:02.510
He's provoking you on purpose.

31:02.510 --> 31:04.570
Fu Xinshu, quit playing the nice guy.

31:05.000 --> 31:06.200
It makes me sick.

31:07.790 --> 31:08.750
Wen Chengye,

31:09.200 --> 31:10.000
if you don't want to join us,

31:10.000 --> 31:12.060
why are you here stirring up trouble?

31:14.280 --> 31:16.190
I just can't stand watching you losers

31:16.190 --> 31:18.600
hog public resources and waste time.

31:18.680 --> 31:21.740
If you can't stand it,
then get the school to disband us.

31:41.130 --> 31:42.110
I'm going to keep playing.

31:42.110 --> 31:44.110
Next time I'll blast one right past him.

31:44.110 --> 31:45.970
We can definitely do it next time!

31:46.000 --> 31:47.110
We're all going to
do extra training from now on.

31:47.110 --> 31:48.790
Next time
we'll score right in front of him.

31:48.790 --> 31:50.990
We'll show him what we've got next time!

31:57.310 --> 31:58.350
Time's up.

31:58.350 --> 31:59.350
Training's over.

32:07.480 --> 32:14.370
[Two days ago]

32:18.640 --> 32:19.970
What are you looking at?

32:21.160 --> 32:22.010
Ms. Lin,

32:22.200 --> 32:23.030
can I help you?

32:25.440 --> 32:26.640
Wen Chengye,

32:26.900 --> 32:28.110
I've seen you do it

32:28.110 --> 32:29.160
several times—

32:29.160 --> 32:31.440
skating over
as if it were completely by chance

32:31.440 --> 32:34.100
while everyone else
was busy playing football.

32:34.920 --> 32:36.550
Seems like you've got me all wrong.

32:36.550 --> 32:38.110
That's only because the road here
is good for skating.

32:38.110 --> 32:39.440
I wasn't watching them.

32:46.350 --> 32:47.200
Lower.

32:49.200 --> 32:50.800
Do you want to play football?

32:53.550 --> 32:54.350
Ms. Lin,

32:55.110 --> 32:57.840
don't tell me you want me to
join the football team

32:57.880 --> 32:59.610
and take Chen Weidong's place.

32:59.750 --> 33:00.880
So smart.

33:00.880 --> 33:02.410
You figured it out already.

33:03.680 --> 33:05.880
Everyone knows that your third-rate team

33:05.880 --> 33:08.110
has a temporary player
who could leave at any time.

33:08.110 --> 33:09.240
So, are you willing?

33:12.640 --> 33:15.500
I just love watching them
make fools of themselves.

33:15.750 --> 33:17.200
But the team's about to be disbanded.

33:17.200 --> 33:18.930
There's not much left to watch.

33:21.440 --> 33:23.160
The team doesn't have to be disbanded.

33:23.160 --> 33:24.400
But we need your help.

33:26.160 --> 33:27.090
What do you mean?

33:27.960 --> 33:30.000
If you pretend to join the team,

33:30.400 --> 33:31.790
it'll provoke them

33:31.790 --> 33:33.850
and bring out their fighting spirit.

33:38.110 --> 33:40.220
Don't you want to see for yourself

33:40.440 --> 33:42.750
just how badly they'll lose
with you standing right in front of them?

33:42.750 --> 33:43.690
Especially

33:43.830 --> 33:45.720
with internationally renowned coach

33:45.720 --> 33:47.480
Wilfred guiding them.

34:03.590 --> 34:04.750
What's in it for me?

34:06.590 --> 34:07.550
What do you want?

34:10.190 --> 34:11.510
What if I said

34:12.030 --> 34:14.889
I want to rank first
in the grade on the monthly exam?

34:16.630 --> 34:18.150
A former top scorer
in the college entrance exam

34:18.150 --> 34:20.350
should be qualified to help you, right?

34:20.880 --> 34:21.480
Okay.

34:21.480 --> 34:22.190
Deal.

34:23.510 --> 34:24.840
What do you want me to do?

34:26.110 --> 34:28.110
See Qin Ao and the others over there?

34:28.510 --> 34:29.770
I want you

34:29.920 --> 34:32.429
to score right in front of them...

34:34.630 --> 34:36.290
and then rub it in their faces.

34:38.190 --> 34:38.920
No problem.

34:50.230 --> 34:51.190
Look,

34:51.190 --> 34:53.230
the moment Wen Chengye showed up,
they all came alive.

34:53.230 --> 34:55.400
It's like throwing
a predatory fish into a pond—

34:55.400 --> 34:57.230
it brings out
everyone's competitive instinct.

34:57.230 --> 34:58.760
That's the catfish effect.

35:00.030 --> 35:00.960
But are you sure

35:00.960 --> 35:02.710
you can give your catfish

35:03.150 --> 35:04.400
what he wants?

35:17.400 --> 35:18.710
Heartless.

35:19.000 --> 35:20.030
Ungrateful!

35:20.030 --> 35:21.230
Shameless!

35:21.880 --> 35:22.680
Open it for me!

35:26.710 --> 35:27.480
Fu,

35:27.710 --> 35:28.760
aren't you going to class?

35:28.760 --> 35:29.760
Going to class?

35:30.030 --> 35:32.320
It's physics class.
Can you even understand it?

35:32.320 --> 35:34.000
I seriously don't get

35:34.110 --> 35:35.150
why the bullet

35:35.150 --> 35:37.400
has to hit a cart going uphill.

35:37.400 --> 35:39.230
What does the cart's speed
have to do with me?

35:39.230 --> 35:40.960
You want it to hit you
instead of the cart?

35:40.960 --> 35:42.150
Can you shut up?

35:42.150 --> 35:43.510
Even if we don't understand it,

35:43.510 --> 35:45.510
Fu will still take notes seriously.

35:48.480 --> 35:50.230
Have you guys ever thought about the fact

35:50.230 --> 35:52.290
that our team only has 10 players now?

35:52.670 --> 35:54.000
And you all know

35:54.110 --> 35:55.110
our level.

35:55.110 --> 35:56.880
We can still enjoy football.

35:58.550 --> 36:00.190
Have you thought about your future?

36:00.190 --> 36:02.050
Follow in my parents' footsteps.

36:02.110 --> 36:03.190
My dad said

36:03.370 --> 36:05.760
working the assembly line
beats being office staff.

36:05.760 --> 36:07.360
I'll just take it as it comes.

36:09.320 --> 36:11.710
I want to become an esports player!

36:15.840 --> 36:17.360
Though I'm probably not cut out for it.

36:17.360 --> 36:18.760
Oh, you actually know that?

36:18.760 --> 36:20.480
An esports player?

36:20.480 --> 36:23.010
Whoever ends up with you
is really out of luck.

36:24.100 --> 36:25.700
I want something else to eat.

36:26.840 --> 36:28.110
This one looks tastier.

36:28.110 --> 36:29.400
-What do you want?
-That one.

36:29.400 --> 36:30.330
Get it yourself.

36:31.630 --> 36:32.430
Boss,

36:32.430 --> 36:34.590
are you really planning to
work in a factory in the future?

36:34.590 --> 36:35.360
Yeah.

36:35.360 --> 36:37.150
And when I do,
I'll rule the whole factory.

36:37.150 --> 36:40.410
If your esports career doesn't work out,
I'll support you.

36:42.230 --> 36:43.030
Fu.

36:45.280 --> 36:47.210
What do you want to do in the future?

36:48.230 --> 36:49.490
I want to go to college.

36:50.800 --> 36:52.330
My mom's not in good health.

36:53.110 --> 36:54.810
I think if I get into college,

36:55.070 --> 36:56.730
she might be a little happier.

36:57.030 --> 36:57.840
Fu,

36:58.510 --> 37:00.550
we've been buddies for so many years,

37:00.550 --> 37:01.760
and this is the first time

37:01.760 --> 37:03.960
I've ever heard you talk about your mom.

37:07.230 --> 37:08.440
She...

37:11.840 --> 37:14.240
She's barely visited since she remarried.

37:16.110 --> 37:17.800
You two don't get along?

37:21.440 --> 37:24.360
I don't know if you still remember
back in middle school.

37:24.360 --> 37:26.220
You skipped breakfast back then,

37:26.510 --> 37:27.510
and your mom chased you all the way

37:27.510 --> 37:29.570
from home to school with buns in hand.

37:30.550 --> 37:31.950
Didn't you think that was

37:32.110 --> 37:33.070
so embarrassing at the time?

37:33.070 --> 37:34.400
Of course I remember!

37:35.070 --> 37:37.130
Do you know why I look up to you so much?

37:37.840 --> 37:39.120
At that time,

37:39.230 --> 37:41.490
everyone made fun of my mom for being fat.

37:42.110 --> 37:43.360
Only Fu,

37:43.360 --> 37:44.550
for my sake,

37:44.550 --> 37:47.010
fell out
with a whole bunch of people over it.

37:47.800 --> 37:49.260
He truly sorted them out.

37:49.400 --> 37:50.950
He had real guts.

37:51.030 --> 37:52.840
Such a mild-mannered guy,

37:53.360 --> 37:55.080
but fierce on the inside.

37:56.550 --> 37:58.230
Now do you know why?

38:09.030 --> 38:10.690
I don't mean to criticize you.

38:10.760 --> 38:13.820
How can a mother
just give birth and not raise her child?

38:14.150 --> 38:16.510
Mom, it's not that I didn't want to
raise him.

38:16.510 --> 38:18.670
My husband told me to
make a clean break with Fu Haisheng,

38:18.670 --> 38:20.550
or he'd divorce me.

38:21.880 --> 38:24.070
You can cut Fu Haisheng out of your life,

38:24.070 --> 38:26.330
but you can't do the same with your child.

38:27.510 --> 38:29.510
I'll leave him in your care, Mom.

38:40.920 --> 38:42.760
I wish I had a mother

38:43.230 --> 38:45.320
by my side like you do.

38:48.800 --> 38:51.440
Things are a bit better between us now,

38:52.850 --> 38:54.770
but I always feel like

38:54.800 --> 38:56.000
she's avoiding me.

38:57.480 --> 38:58.070
I...

38:58.070 --> 38:59.790
I really want to work hard,

39:00.030 --> 39:02.880
s-study well, and get into college.

39:04.710 --> 39:06.710
But no matter how hard I try,

39:06.710 --> 39:08.640
I can't even break into the top 300.

39:13.880 --> 39:14.930
So...

39:15.960 --> 39:18.020
that's why you want to play football—

39:18.200 --> 39:19.880
to get into college as a student athlete.

39:19.880 --> 39:20.680
Yes.

39:21.030 --> 39:22.510
It's my only way out.

39:23.110 --> 39:25.570
It's the only way
I can prove myself to my mom.

39:35.070 --> 39:35.830
Well...

39:36.030 --> 39:38.110
T-This is my own business.

39:39.760 --> 39:43.820
I shouldn't keep dragging you all into this
just to play football with me.

39:44.360 --> 39:46.000
I-I'm going to class.

39:55.320 --> 39:57.250
Your buddy, Ao, will play with you.

39:57.320 --> 39:59.120
It's just more practice, right?

39:59.710 --> 40:00.440
Yeah.

40:00.710 --> 40:02.400
Football isn't just your business!

40:02.400 --> 40:04.660
We firmly stand behind Boss's decision!

40:14.110 --> 40:15.880
Alright, I'm going to class.

40:17.400 --> 40:18.550
Take notes properly, alright?

40:18.550 --> 40:20.550
I need to copy them when you get back.

40:28.710 --> 40:32.280
One, two, three, four, five, six,
seven, eight, nine, ten...

40:35.360 --> 40:36.190
Ms. Lin.

40:40.800 --> 40:42.410
Didn't we agree yesterday

40:42.630 --> 40:44.430
that I would come find you today?

40:44.800 --> 40:46.200
Everything's prepared.

40:47.880 --> 40:49.110
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

40:54.080 --> 40:54.850
[Senior Year
First Semester Diagnostic Exam]

40:54.850 --> 40:58.380
[Name: Lin Wanxing]

41:04.410 --> 41:06.870
You're giving me test papers
from years ago?

41:06.880 --> 41:07.940
And they're yours.

41:08.030 --> 41:10.490
Are you sure
I can get first place with these?

41:11.480 --> 41:12.400
Absolutely.

41:12.400 --> 41:13.670
I spent ages looking for them.

41:13.670 --> 41:15.510
Those are all classic question types.

41:15.510 --> 41:18.110
They'll definitely help
improve your grades.

41:18.880 --> 41:19.630
Ms. Lin.

41:22.500 --> 41:23.910
You promised me

41:25.030 --> 41:26.430
you'd help me come first,

41:27.000 --> 41:29.600
or else you can quit
being the team supervisor.

41:29.920 --> 41:32.360
I wonder if you've ever heard of

41:32.360 --> 41:34.800
Edward Hall's theory of personal space.

41:38.400 --> 41:39.330
What do you mean?

41:42.030 --> 41:43.450
I mean,

41:43.510 --> 41:44.910
given your personality,

41:45.190 --> 41:47.390
you normally keep people at a distance.

41:47.590 --> 41:49.880
But you're standing
so close to me right now

41:49.880 --> 41:52.340
that it's beyond what's considered normal.

41:56.030 --> 41:57.840
If I'm not mistaken,

41:57.840 --> 41:58.960
Wen,

41:58.960 --> 42:00.110
you're trying so hard

42:00.110 --> 42:01.360
to stop me from being the supervisor

42:01.360 --> 42:04.020
because you don't want
the team rebuilt, right?

42:13.090 --> 42:14.770
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

42:15.710 --> 42:17.200
♪ Because you're with me ♪

42:19.950 --> 42:21.480
♪ The light shimmers ♪

42:22.730 --> 42:24.040
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

42:25.670 --> 42:26.810
♪ Running towards you ♪

42:27.600 --> 42:28.860
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪
